Class Collideable

  • java.lang.Object
    • Collideable
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Fish, Garbage, Hoop

    public abstract class Collideable
extends java.lang.Object
    Collideable abstract class. This is an abstract class that represents an object that can collide with the dolphin or the net
